#VERAfied: Several social media users, including former ABS-CBN broadcaster Jay Sonza, shared on Facebook an altered photo of an ABS-CBN News van, falsely claiming it overturned  as Typhoon Ulysses raged over Luzon on Nov. 12.

text.1:
#VERAfied: A viral video showing rampaging waters supposedly from dams that released water in Cagayan during #UlyssesPH is false.

All four clips in the 46-second video show different instances of flooding in Laos and Thailand. #factcheckph
